
There is a white dragon and a red dragon.\nThe white dragon goes to a computer manufacturing genius and asks him to make a computer so powerful that it can simulate reality.\nThe computer manufacturing genius makes a computer so powerful that it can simulate the entire universe and everything in it.\nThe computer system is left with no password.\nThe red dragon finds it, and gets closer and says there's no way I'm going in there.\nThe he decides to go in.\nThey ran the computer system for a really long time.\nAnd the red dragon got stuck inside it because he really liked it there.\nThe white dragon destroyed all the computers in some massive destruction.

